<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛毛虫终于对爱丽丝说话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？” 他用犯困的声音问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这不是一个好的开头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝害羞地回答：“我不知道，先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天早上起来，我还知道自己是谁，但是之后我变了好几次。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么意思？解释给我听听。” 毛毛虫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然毛毛虫看上去很没有礼貌，爱丽丝还是试着礼貌地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思，先生，我没有办法解释得更详细了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在一天里不断地变大变小让我觉得很困惑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不会啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能你还没有机会知道。” 爱丽丝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当你变成蝴蝶的时候，你很可能也会觉得奇怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会啊！” 毛毛虫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可能跟我的感觉不一样。” 爱丽丝仍然尽量保持礼貌地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是对我来说，变成蝴蝶会是一件非常奇怪的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你！” 毛毛虫说，“你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的对话又回到了起点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝对毛毛虫的话感到很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她挺直了自己的身体，盯着毛毛虫说：“我觉得你应该先告诉我你是谁！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么呀？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这又是一个很难回答的问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛毛虫的心情很不好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝想要离开了，她开始往其他地方走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回来！” 毛毛虫对她叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有重要的事情跟你说！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝挺感兴趣。于是她走回来，等毛毛虫说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要发脾气。” 毛毛虫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就这样？” 爱丽丝非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好几分钟过去了，毛毛虫就静静地坐在那里，不理爱丽丝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝又打算离开了，但她其实也没有什么事情可做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，她决定继续等待。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许毛毛虫还是会说出什么有趣的事情来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛毛虫终于又说话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以你觉得自己变了?”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的” 。爱丽丝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很高兴毛毛虫终于听到她说的话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一开始我变大了，然后我又变小了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每几分钟我都会变一次。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛毛虫打量了一下爱丽丝。“你想变成多大？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不在乎。我只是不喜欢一直这样变来变去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你知道吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道啊！” 毛毛虫回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝什么也没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从来没有见过这么不友好的动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她要发脾气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛毛虫打断了她的思路。“那你现在满意吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想要变大，因为三英寸是个让人讨厌的高度。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“三英寸是个完美的高度！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛毛虫站起来，让爱丽丝看到他刚好就是三英寸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我根本就不习惯！” 爱丽丝抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很快就会习惯了。” 毛毛虫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝等了等，希望毛毛虫能多说些话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等到最后，他只是打了两次哈欠，摇了摇身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他从蘑菇上爬了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一边能让你变大。” 毛毛虫说，“一边能让你变小。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝不知道他在说什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么的一边？什么的另一边？” 她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蘑菇啊！” 毛毛虫回答，好像爱丽丝刚才把问题问出声了一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，他就不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>